      <h3>I architect <em>AI-driven analytics</em> systems that ship in production and outlive me.</h3>
      <p>UK-based digital technology specialist. I design and build proprietary analytics and AI-automation systems — forecasters, sentiment engines, anomaly detectors, organic-insight automation — that <b>50+ teams</b> use on a weekly cadence. Independent product founder, public technical author, peer reviewer.</p>
      <p>My work sits at the intersection of <b>AI / machine learning</b>, <b>data engineering</b>, and <b>digital measurement</b>. Verbatim client outcomes documented from <b>BBC, General Mills (Blue Buffalo), Diligent Pharma</b> and <b>MRI Management</b>. Long-form technical writing published in <b>Cointelegraph</b>. Quoted as an expert source by <b>CCN</b>. Invited chapter reviewer for <b>IGI Global</b>.</p>
      <p>Current research sits at <b>AI-search disruption to organic visibility</b>, <b>analytics QA automation</b>, <b>consent-mode transparency</b>, and <b>measurement-platform accountability</b>. Drafts in flight; methodology open.</p>

